{"tid":283032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[盜亦有道]竊賊趁風爆竊食肆掠5000元　「員工小費」原封不動","createTime":"2017-06-13T22:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T23:42:54.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a69400db8600ffe56c67f18decbd38a4dd815c8b","tid":283032,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:00:44.000Z","msg":"油麻地彌敦道499號地下一間台式食肆，早上10時許，職員上班準備開舖時，發現收銀機被撬毀，櫃枱一片凌亂，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，發現店舖後門被人撬毀，相信賊人於凌晨由後巷天井位爬入，再撬門犯案。經點算後，證實損失約5000元現金。不過，收銀櫃枱內一包內有數百元的「員工小費」則未被取走，食肆職員均嘖嘖稱奇。在場調查警員則打趣道：「留返畀你哋！」"},{"pid":"b9e4c3c108922584a6ab04594228881080e43fc3","tid":283032,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:01:19.000Z","msg":"案件列作爆竊，交由油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170613/s00001/1497328708740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170613%2Fs00001%2F1497328708740&d=sOdAtgzxSNOGM087bcBtqDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=6c00a75e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170613%2Fs00001%2F1497328708740&h=3b0ccf14\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170613/s00001/1497328708740</a>"},{"pid":"61c1ece5d499cf5820e485cdc71d4fb6d25cb948","tid":283032,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:18:31.000Z","msg":"老闆：要用黎彌補損失"},{"pid":"009d6648a0c9e8d018d02c6ff5bf8badbbdb4beb","tid":283032,"uid":57204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老闆：要用黎彌補損失</blockquote><br />\n裡應外合爆多佢一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c565031b5f10d1526c4a3807c3dfb8544a6fc37","tid":283032,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老闆：要用黎彌補損失</blockquo